I find #2325 helps a lot.  如何在折线图中默认平铺模式而不是堆积模式？ #2325 
Inside the "change to line", set stack value to '' (see the code below). It will make change to line default is tiled no matter comes from tiled or stack. 
Also #3004 talks about the same thing.  堆积折线图 有bug #3004 
The root reason behind is the common users are expecting the tiled line when click the line. Stack line is actually a bonus which most users are not aware of. So it's better to keep the feature but make tiled the default effect.

